<h3 id="what-is-apache">What is <a href="https://httpd.apache.org/">Apache</a>?</h3>
<p>Apache Web Server is a software package that turns a computer into an HTTP server. That is, it sends web pages â€“ stored as HTML files â€“ to people on the internet who request them. It is open-source software, which means it can be used and modified freely.</p>

